data.text: @YvetteRMartinez I feel the exact same way. The book has gotten horrible reviews anyway, so I’m glad I didn’t waste my money. 😉 (There was sneak peak of it on one site & it was very poorly written.)

@SarahSaysS0 Exactly!! I was going to buy her book, but I'm not interested anymore. Bums me out because I liked her. I hope the reunion isn't an hour of them ganging up on Teddi. That always pisses me off.

@YvetteRMartinez I totally agree!! Overall, I think Teddi is just too nice for the show. Dorit is awful and it’s so disappointing that Erika has decided to help her bring Teddi down. It’s so hypocritical of everything she says she stands for. 😒
@SarahSaysS0 Poor Teddi. And in regards to Erika, what a disappointment she's becoming...I used to like her so much.
